r />\n3. 要罷就要早啲起身, 攞地鐵早乘優惠.<br />\n4. 地鐵唔好塞死一個站, 係䌓忙轉車點係咁上落搭來回車. <br />\n5. 路面繼續慢駛, 迴旋處行唔到直線<br />\n6. 提早出門去自由行地點鳩烏<br />\n7. 要去機場接朋友"},{"pid":"a0910f770926bf32f0171fc2a75bf37359d41d20","tid":1449380,"uid":61655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:36:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"575e57c0f145a849461b64a275461f330b1743ad","tid":1449380,"uid":61655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:37:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6675c9502cd905cfbe938d82c5dbd6d14331c107","tid":1449380,"uid":61655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d60b7484743e7112ef7d0fbe297386994c5cf1e5","tid":1449380,"uid":61655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:38:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4907cc8f95b856b2887b4acb545042fa30e6f88","tid":1449380,"uid":264188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:39:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02e70055fb7e7d720c0ee47ca6c248e8546d2f5c","tid":1449380,"uid":61655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4362f32d1922de0aa89151f937c4c7554f2d87a5","tid":1449380,"uid":61655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:40:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70ed6db5dd78474ad105ef49b03abfe59d19ee6c","tid":1449380,"uid":278285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:40:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n黑警以眼還眼<br />\n五大訴求決一不可 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6hOXuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6hOXuf.jpg&h=407618c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70hjjHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70hjjHC.jpg&h=04649361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有白宮聯署 要求medical army支援 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-h